speaker:
FIRST
               
              GENTLEMAN
text: Did you ever hear the like?

speaker:
SECOND
               
              GENTLEMAN
text: No, nor never shall do in such a

speaker:
SECOND
               
              GENTLEMAN
text: place as this, she being once gone.

speaker:
FIRST
               
              GENTLEMAN
text: But to have divinity preached there!

speaker:
FIRST
               
              GENTLEMAN
text: Did you ever dream of such a thing?

speaker:
SECOND
               
              GENTLEMAN
text: No, no. Come, I am for no more

speaker:
SECOND
               
              GENTLEMAN
text: bawdy houses. Shall ’s go hear the vestals sing?

speaker:
FIRST
               
              GENTLEMAN
text: I’ll do anything now that is virtuous,

speaker:
FIRST
               
              GENTLEMAN
text: but I am out of the road of rutting forever.
